svg.desc: The chart shows participation in further education by age group in 2007 and 2016. Participation in further training stood at 43 percent in 2007 and 50 percent in 2016. This increase can be recognised in all age groups, but is particularly pronounced in the age group 55-64. Between 2007 and 2016, participation increased from 27 to 44 percent for those aged 55-64.

div.p:
Source: Adult Education Survey 2007 and 2016.
